$ $GIT_COMMON_DIR

If set, the following files are used under `$GIT_COMMON_DIR` instead of under → development/version-control-systems/git/_git:
  • → development/version-control-systems/git/_git/objects
  • → development/version-control-systems/git/_git/packed-refs
  • → development/version-control-systems/git/_git/config
  • → development/version-control-systems/git/_git/branches
  • → development/version-control-systems/git/_git/hooks
  • .git/remotes (?)
  • → development/version-control-systems/git/_git/shallow
  • → development/version-control-systems/git/_git/worktrees

sa:
  → development/version-control-systems/git/_git/commondir

